text: Ronan Byrne (born 17 April 1998) is an Irish rower. He won a medal at the 2019 World Rowing Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results He won the gold medal at the 2019 European Rowing U23 Championships in Ioannina. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male rowers Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for Ireland
